{"lemma":"شُراةً","slug":"شُراةً","root":"ش.ر.#","root_slug":"ش-ر-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ر-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22259","n22270"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8F%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%A9%D9%8B"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22259","headword_ar":"شَرَاهُ","root":"$rY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$irFY","text_ar":"شِرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iraA='N","text_ar":"شِرَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * Mgh, Msb, * TA,) the former inf. n. the more in repute, (Msb, TA,) and this is of the dial. of Nejd, the latter being of the dial. of El-Hijáz, or the latter may be said to be with medd for the purpose of assimilating it to a preceding word, accord. to El-Munádee, or it may be regarded as an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAraAhu","text_ar":"شَارَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAEahu","text_ar":"بَاعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the sense in which this is generally used, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sold it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, Mgh, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he gave it for a price:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$otaraAhu","text_ar":"اِشْتَرَاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the sense in which this is generally used, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he bought it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, Mgh;) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araAhu","text_ar":"شَرَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acquired it, for a price:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or this and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$trAh","text_ar":"اشتراه","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"both signify"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAEahu","text_ar":"بَاعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sold it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (T, * K, TA;) but the former is more used than the latter in this sense: (T, TA:) and both signify also ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he bought it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he possessed it by sale;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) which is the more usual meaning of the latter: (T, TA:) thus the former has two contr. meanings, (S, Msb, K,) and the latter also: (K:) for the two persons selling and buying sell and buy the price and the thing upon which the price is put; so that each of the things given in exchange is sold in one point of view and bought in another. (Msb, TA.) It is said in the Kur [ii. 203],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamina A@ln~aAsi mano ya$oriY","text_ar":"وَمِنَ ا@لنَّاسِ مَنْ يَشْرِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafosahu A@botigaA='a maroDaApi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"نَفْسَهُ ا@بْتِغَا=ءَ مَرْضَاةِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And of men is he"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who sells"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"himself in the endeavour to obtain the approval of God"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, * TA.) And in the same, [xii. 20],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa$arawohu bivamanK baxosK","text_ar":"وَشَرَوْهُ بِثَمَنٍ بَخْسٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they sold him"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for a deficient,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an insufficient, price"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) And in the same [ii. 15],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uwlaAy^ika A@l~a*iyna","text_ar":"اُولَايِكَ ا@لَّذِينَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@lD~alaAlapa biA@lohudaY","text_ar":"ا@لضَّلَالَةَ بِا@لْهُدَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@$otarawuA","text_ar":"ا@شْتَرَوُا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@$otarayuwA","text_ar":"ا@شْتَرَيُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) [lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Those are they who have purchased error with right direction,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who have taken"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlDlAlp","text_ar":"الضلالة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in exchange for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlhdY","text_ar":"الهدى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ksh, Bd, Jel:) or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who have preferred"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlDlAlp","text_ar":"الضلالة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlhdY","text_ar":"الهدى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ksh, Bd:) [for] of any one who relinquishes a thing and lays hold upon another thing, one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$trAh","text_ar":"اشتراه"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) which is thus tropically used [as meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took it in exchange"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bigayorihi","text_ar":"بِغَيْرِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by"},{"kind":"text","text":"giving up"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"another thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;) and hence this saying in the Kur-án. (K, TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araY binafosihi","text_ar":"شَرَى بِنَفْسِهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani Alqawomi","text_ar":"عَنِ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He advanced before the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to their enemy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and fought in defence of them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he advanced to the Sultán, and spoke for the people:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) [as though he sold himself for them; the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bnfsh","text_ar":"بنفسه"},{"kind":"text","text":"being app. redundant:] or, as in the Tekmileh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araY binafosihi A_ilaY Alqawomi","text_ar":"شَرَى بِنَفْسِهِ اـِلَى القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he advanced to the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, and fought them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araY","text_ar":"شَرَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnFA","text_ar":"فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$irFY","text_ar":"شِرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He mocked at, scoffed at, laughed at, derided,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ridiculed, such a one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [and] so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ar~aAhu","text_ar":"شَرَّاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jad~aEahu","text_ar":"جَدَّعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.: thus there written, perhaps for the purpose of assimilating it to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jad~aEahu","text_ar":"جَدَّعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"].) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arogamahu","text_ar":"اَرْغَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He angered such a one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did evil to him, and angered him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Lh, K, TA:) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aworamahu","text_ar":"اَوْرَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaTaAhu","text_ar":"غَطَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or perhaps"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaZaAhu","text_ar":"عَظَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for both are expl. alike]: all said of God. (Lh, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEala","text_ar":"فَعَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi maA $araAhu","text_ar":"بِهِ مَا شَرَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did to him that which occasioned evil to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which displeased, grieved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vexed, him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saA='ahu","text_ar":"سَا=ءَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHaAhu A@ll~`hu wa$araAhu","text_ar":"لَحَاهُ ا@للّٰهُ وَشَرَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God remove him far from good"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prosperity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"curse him, and do evil to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"displease"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grieve"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vex him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araY A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"شَرَى ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnFA","text_ar":"فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$irFY","text_ar":"شِرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God smote him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may God smite him, with the eruption termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arFY","text_ar":"شَرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (K, TA.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araAhu","text_ar":"شَرَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$irFY","text_ar":"شِرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ar~arahu","text_ar":"شَرَّرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spread it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to dry"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;) [in copies of the K, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$r","text_ar":"شر"},{"kind":"text","text":", written, in this sense, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ar~aAhu","text_ar":"شَرَّاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";] namely, flesh-meat, and a garment, or piece of cloth, and [the preparation of curd called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqiT","text_ar":"اَقِط"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ariYa","text_ar":"شَرِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arFY","text_ar":"شَرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) said of lightning, (S, K, &c.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It shone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gleamed, much:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it shone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gleamed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and spread in the face of the clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as in the T,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became dispersed in the face of the clouds:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$rY","text_ar":"اشرى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; (K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it shone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gleamed, consecutively:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the latter verb mentioned by Sgh. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (S,) said of the nose-rein of a camel, (S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in a state of commotion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of much commotion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) [See also 12.]) ―         -b3-  Also, (K,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, angry:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, flurried by reason of anger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b4-  And, said of evil, or mischief,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It spread,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayonahumo","text_ar":"بَيْنَهُمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became great,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"formidable;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner said of an affair, or event. (Nh, TA. [See also 10.]) ―         -b5-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ast$rY","text_ar":"استشرى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persisted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persevered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in an affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his error, and his corrupt conduct:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the former, said of a man, is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariYa","text_ar":"غَرِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in measure and meaning [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he persisted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persevered, in his anger"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) One says of a horse,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ariYa fiY","text_ar":"شَرِىَ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sayorihi","text_ar":"سَيْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n. as above, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He per-"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1545},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sisted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persevered, in his pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ast$rY","text_ar":"استشرى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he exceeded the usual bounds therein,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and went on without languor:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Eadowihi","text_ar":"فِى عَدْوِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ast$rY","text_ar":"استشرى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(i. e. a horse)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persisted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persevered, in his running:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ariYa fiY lijaAmihi","text_ar":"شَرِىَ فِى لِجَامِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a horse)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strained his bridle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ariyato Eayonuhu biAld~amoEi","text_ar":"شَرِيَتْ عَيْنُهُ بِالدَّمْعِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His eye persisted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persevered, in the shedding of tears, the tears pouring forth consecutively."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ariYa","text_ar":"شَرِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arFY","text_ar":"شَرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his skin, broke out with the eruption termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arFY","text_ar":"شَرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","Mgh","TA","T","Ksh","Bd","Jel","Lh"]},{"entry_id":"n22270","headword_ar":"شَرَاةٌ","root":"$rY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arFY","text_ar":"شَرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}